

goto your github account
create new repo
    - give name to the repo
    - make it public or private repo
    - do not select .gitignore or readme file
    - click on apply / save

verify repo is created ??

Clone repo
=============

copy the gitrepo path, 3 types but you copy https / url

open pycharm / intellij - make sure you are in parent folder like pycharmProject or IntelliJProject

verify current directory - run command - pwd (it gives present working directory)

run command - git clone {url_that_you_copied}

close your IDE and reopen again

select the newly created folder